
Undead Siege project files

Originally exported using MuseScore 4.6.5.
Requires the following MuseSounds packs:
    - Muse Strings
    - Muse Brass
    - Muse Choir
    - Muse Percussion

The makefile guarantees repeatable exports, including loudness tweaks and consistent ogg format. 
Additionally it exports a full score PDF.
